<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Benjamin Gabernig</title>
<meta
name="description"
content="Benjamin Gabernig designs and builds consumer software with a calm product lens, strong systems thinking, and a sharp eye for detail."
/>
<script>
(() => {
const storedTheme = window.localStorage.getItem("theme");
const preferredLight = window.matchMedia("(prefers-color-scheme: light)").matches;
const theme = storedTheme || (preferredLight ? "light" : "dark");
document.documentElement.dataset.theme = theme;
})();
</script>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
<link
href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500;600&family=Instrument+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap"
rel="stylesheet"
/>
<script type="importmap">
{
"imports": {
"three": "/vendor/three/build/three.module.js",
"three/addons/": "/vendor/three/examples/jsm/"
}
}
</script>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />
</head>
<body>
<audio id="soundtrack" src="audio/relax-synth.mp3" preload="metadata" loop playsinline></audio>
<div class="cursor-shell" aria-hidden="true">
<div class="cursor-ring" id="cursor-ring"></div>
<div class="cursor-dot" id="cursor-dot"></div>
<div class="cursor-label" id="cursor-label">open</div>
</div>
<div class="site-frame">
<header class="topbar">
<div class="topbar-progress" id="topbar-progress"></div>
<a class="brand" href="#home" aria-label="Go to homepage">
<span class="brand-mark">BG</span>
<span class="brand-copy">
<strong>benjamin gabernig</strong>
<span>product / design</span>
</span>
</a>

<nav class="topnav" aria-label="Primary">
<a href="#principles">Approach</a>
<a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav>

<div class="topbar-tools">
<button class="theme-toggle soundtrack-toggle" id="soundtrack-toggle" type="button" aria-label="Play soundtrack">
<span class="soundtrack-icon" aria-hidden="true">
<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true">
<path d="M4 9h4l5-4v14l-5-4H4z"></path>
<path d="M16 9.5a4.5 4.5 0 0 1 0 5"></path>
<path d="M18.8 7a8 8 0 0 1 0 10"></path>
</svg>
</span>
<span id="soundtrack-label">play</span>
</button>
<button class="theme-toggle" id="theme-toggle" type="button" aria-label="Toggle color theme">
theme / light
</button>
</div>
</header>

<main id="home">
<section class="hero">
<div class="hero-copy">
<p class="section-label">system 01 / live chamber</p>
<h1>Benjamin Gabernig.</h1>
<p class="hero-intro">I design clear, thoughtful experiences.  Working across countries has taught me to  listen and design for people and planet.</p>

<div class="hero-actions">
<a class="button button-solid" href="#contact">Get in touch</a>
<a class="button button-ghost" href="mailto:benjamin@gabernig.com">Talk to me</a>
</div>

<div class="status-panel">
<p class="status-label">live status</p>
<p class="status-line" id="status-line">
building products with calm edges
</p>
</div>
</div>

<aside class="signal-panel" aria-label="Generative signal diagram">
<div class="signal-topline">
<p>visor feed</p>
<p>forest chamber / probe deck</p>
</div>

<div class="signal-stage" id="signal-stage">
<canvas id="signal-canvas" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
<div class="signal-ceiling" aria-hidden="true"></div>
<div class="signal-floor" aria-hidden="true"></div>

<div class="probe-stack">
<article class="probe-panel probe-panel-left probe-panel-map">
<div class="probe-head">
<p>probe / 01</p>
<p>archive field</p>
</div>
<p class="probe-live" id="probe-field-live">depth axis / stable</p>
<p class="probe-note" id="probe-field-note">signal archive / chamber specimen map</p>
<canvas class="probe-canvas" data-viz="fieldprobe" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
</article>

<article class="probe-panel probe-panel-right probe-panel-right-top">
<div class="probe-head">
<p>probe / 02</p>
<p>vortex readout</p>
</div>
<p class="probe-live" id="probe-swirl-live">waterfall pulse / low</p>
<p class="probe-note" id="probe-swirl-note">pulse monitor / environmental intake</p>
<canvas class="probe-canvas" data-viz="swirl" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
</article>

<article class="probe-panel probe-panel-right probe-panel-right-bottom probe-panel-geometry">
<div class="probe-head">
<p>probe / 03</p>
<p>section geometry</p>
</div>
<p class="probe-live" id="probe-section-live">lock vector / idle</p>
<p class="probe-note" id="probe-section-note">azimuth frame / chamber section cut</p>
<canvas class="probe-canvas" data-viz="gridslice" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
</article>
</div>

<div class="signal-overlay">
<div class="signal-marker-block">
<div class="signal-marker">
<p>chamber / 01</p>
<p>slow drift / synthetic woodland / live capture</p>
</div>
<div class="zoom-controls" aria-label="Chamber zoom presets">
<p class="zoom-label">zoom</p>
<div class="zoom-buttons">
<button class="zoom-button" type="button" data-zoom-level="wide">01</button>
<button class="zoom-button" type="button" data-zoom-level="field">02</button>
<button class="zoom-button" type="button" data-zoom-level="close">03</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="signal-readout signal-readout-min">
<p id="signal-readout-text">depth:+24 / lock:soft / feed:stable</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</aside>
</section>

<section class="transfer-band" aria-label="Chamber transfer readout">
<p class="transfer-kicker">transfer / 01</p>
<p class="transfer-copy">field extraction / archive handoff</p>
<p class="transfer-readout" id="transfer-readout">handoff / zoom:03 / pulse:31% / sweep:+0.08</p>
</section>

<section class="metrics" aria-label="Highlights">
<article class="metric">
<p class="metric-label">focus</p>
<p class="metric-value">consumer software</p>
</article>
<article class="metric">
<p class="metric-label">shipping</p>
<p class="metric-value">Untired</p>
</article>
<article class="metric">
<p class="metric-label">building</p>
<p class="metric-value">Soba</p>
</article>
<article class="metric">
<p class="metric-label">discipline</p>
<p class="metric-value">product / design</p>
</article>
</section>

<section class="visual-band" aria-label="Visual systems">
<article class="visual-card visual-card-wide">
<div class="visual-head">
<p class="section-label">system 02 / field</p>
<p>signal archive</p>
</div>
<canvas class="mini-canvas" data-viz="field" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
</article>

<article class="visual-card visual-card-note">
<div class="visual-head">
<p class="section-label">system 02 / note</p>
<p>terrain</p>
</div>
<p class="visual-note">
Built for attention, play, and care.
</p>
</article>
</section>


<section class="section-heading split-heading">
<div>
<p class="section-label">system 04 / operating notes</p>
<h2 id="principles">How I work.</h2>
</div>
<p class="section-note">Start with behavior. Keep it clear. Make it feel alive.</p>
</section>

<section class="principles-grid">
<article class="principle">
<div class="principle-top">
<p class="principle-index">01</p>
<canvas class="principle-canvas" data-viz="orbit" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
</div>
<h3>Start with behavior</h3>
<p>The job comes first. The interface should serve the product, not distract from it.</p>
</article>

<article class="principle">
<div class="principle-top">
<p class="principle-index">02</p>
<canvas class="principle-canvas" data-viz="grid" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
</div>
<h3>Reduce with edge</h3>
<p>Strip it back until the point is obvious, but keep enough character for it to feel human.</p>
</article>

<article class="principle">
<div class="principle-top">
<p class="principle-index">03</p>
<canvas class="principle-canvas" data-viz="branch" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
</div>
<h3>Make the system legible</h3>
<p>Structure, states, and labels should teach the product on first contact.</p>
</article>

<article class="principle">
<div class="principle-top">
<p class="principle-index">04</p>
<canvas class="principle-canvas" data-viz="pulse" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
</div>
<h3>Use motion as state</h3>
<p>Motion should guide timing, focus, and feedback, not compete for attention.</p>
</article>
</section>

<section class="about-band">
<div class="about-copy">
<p class="section-label">system 05 / what i do</p>
<h2>I work across product and design.</h2>
<p>I like shaping the whole thing: behavior, interface, systems, and the way it ships.</p>
</div>

<div class="about-panel">
<div class="visual-head">
<p class="about-panel-label">right now</p>
<p>products + interactive systems</p>
</div>
<canvas class="mini-canvas mini-canvas-short" data-viz="studio" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
<p class="about-panel-copy">
I am especially drawn to games, digital wellbeing, ambient companionship, and gentle AI.
</p>
</div>
</section>

<section class="footer-band" aria-label="Signal footer">
<div class="footer-band-copy">
<p class="section-label">system 06 / stack</p>
<h2>I work across the full stack.</h2>
<p class="footer-band-note">
Web, mobile, backend, database, 3D, and hardware. I am comfortable moving across the whole product, not just one layer.
</p>
<div class="residue-readout" aria-label="Residue readout">
<p><span>web</span><strong>interfaces / systems / product surfaces</strong></p>
<p><span>mobile</span><strong>native app flows / interaction detail</strong></p>
<p><span>backend</span><strong>services / logic / infrastructure glue</strong></p>
<p><span>database</span><strong>schema / queries / data shape</strong></p>
<p><span>3d</span><strong>three.js / spatial interaction / realtime scenes</strong></p>
<p><span>hardware</span><strong>device thinking / physical interfaces / integration</strong></p>
</div>
</div>
<canvas class="mini-canvas mini-canvas-footer" data-viz="footer" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
</section>
</main>

<footer class="footer footer-bleed" id="contact">
<div class="footer-shell">
<div class="footer-grid">
<div class="footer-portal">
<canvas class="mini-canvas contact-canvas" data-viz="contact" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
</div>

<div class="footer-main">
<p class="section-label">system 07 / open channel</p>
<h2>Need someone who can design and build?</h2>
<p class="footer-cta-copy">
I help turn rough ideas into clear, shippable products.
</p>
</div>

<div class="footer-action">
<p class="footer-kicker">email to start</p>
<a class="footer-mail" href="mailto:benjamin@gabernig.com">benjamin@gabernig.com</a>
<p class="footer-subcopy">
Send the brief, the prototype, or the messy version.
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="footer-rail" aria-label="Open channel details">
<p><span>open for</span><strong>product / design</strong></p>
<p><span>works on</span><strong>web / mobile / backend / 3d / hardware</strong></p>
<p><span>mode</span><strong>collaborative / independent / fractional</strong></p>
</div>

<p class="footer-note">
<span id="year"></span> / benjamin gabernig
</p>
</div>
</footer>

</div>

